bio:
Your best interior design app.
The fastest way to create a professional interior design. Floor plans, HQ visualizations, VR tours, shopping list, architect statistics, auto PDF report - everything you need in one app.
Even newcomers can create interiors and sell it with Home Planner.
https://icandesignapp.com/app

I started Show Home Lighting because I wanted to make an easy to install track lighting kit that could run the famous WLED firmware, and that meets electrical code. We finally have a product ready to be available to the public. Check out my website showhomelighting.com for more info. 
Thanks!

Make your home a better place 🏡

Planner 5D is a home improvement and interior design platform trusted by over 95M+ people on mobile and desktop. Create your own interior plans without any special skills.

In Planner 5D, you can collaborate on the same project with others, share your project looks with friends, add real furniture from integrated manufacturer catalogs, export high-resolution images, and much more.

Planner 5D is your real chance to transform the boring task of creating interior layouts into an interesting and effortless process.

Planner 5D — Interior Design App:
📐 Create floor plans and interior designs in 2D & 3D.
🌟 Visualize your design in virtual reality.
🛠️ DIY with Planner 5D — the future of interior design.

At Cree Lighting, we don’t just make lights—we revolutionize your relationship with light.
